nodes.text: Khomm sliders were one of the standard sliders on the menu at Dex's Diner on the planet Coruscant. They were inspired by the planet Khomm and its native species the Khommite's tendency toward perfectionism. It consisted of a precisely measured amount of strider cheese sauce and a single Mongo beefhead patty all on a trans-shipped medium-density food-board. It cost 6.5 credits.
